"https://www.facebook.com/BrentwoodSchoolUK/" class="nav-socials-fb" title="Facebook" target="_blank">Facebook</a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/Brentwood_Sch" class="nav-socials-tw" title="Twitter" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/brentwood_sch/" class="nav-socials-it" title="Instagram" target="_blank">Instagram</a></li><li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMHNs-j5OswTUSUeMAiAoLw" class="nav-socials-yt" title="YouTube" target="_blank">YouTube</a></li></ul><h4>/Brentwood_Sch</h4></div></div></div><input type="hidden" id="MediaPlusFeedsArray" value="[&#34;8499&#34;,&#34;8500&#34;,&#34;8501&#34;,&#34;8503&#34;,&#34;8505&#34;,&#34;8506&#34;]"> <input type="hidden" id="MediaFeedTags" value="[&#34;alumni&#34;,&#34;Old Brentwoods&#34;,&#34;#oldbrentwoods&#34;,&#34;#stayconnected&#34;,&#34;OB&#34;,&#34;Obs&#34;]"> <input type="hidden" id="SecondLevelMediaAndFilter" value="OR"> <input type="hidden" id="SecondLevelMediaFullTextFilter" value="True"> <input type="hidden" id="MediaPlusFeedsArray" value="[&#34;8499&#34;,&#34;8500&#34;,&#34;8501&#34;,&#34;8503&#34;,&#34;8505&#34;,&#34;8506&#34;,&#34;15253&#34;,&#34;18052&#34;,&#34;18053&#34;,&#34;18702&#34;,&#34;19970&#34;,&#34;19971&#34;,&#34;19972&#34;]"><div class="slvl-hero"><div class="slvl-hero-container swiper-container"><div class="slvl-hero-wrapper swiper-wrapper"><div class="slvl-hero-preloader swiper-lazy-preloader"></div><div class="slvl-hero-slide swiper-slide swiper-lazy"><div class="slvl-hero-slide-image" style="background-image:url('/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Headers/05-Our-Community/header-old-brentwood.jpg')" data-background="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Headers/05-Our-Community/header-old-brentwood.jpg" title="Old Brentwoods"></div></div></div><h1 class="slvl-hero-pagetitle">Old Brentwoods</h1></div></div><div class="content"><div class="content-section slvl-content-section"><div class="content-section-wrapper slvl-content-section-wrapper"><div class="slvl-content-section-sidebar"><div class="slvl-content-section-sidebar-level slvl-sidenav-section"><h2 class="slvl-content-section-sidebar-title">Our Community</h2><ul class="slvl-sidenav"><li><a href="/our-community/parents/parents-hub" class="">Parents</a><ul><li><a href="/our-community/parents/parents-hub" class="">Parents&#39; Hub</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/parents/term-dates" class="">Term Dates</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/parents/food-at-brentwood" class="">Food at Brentwood</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/parents/tuck-shop" class="">Tuck Shop</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/parents/uniform-shop" class="">Uniform &amp; Shop</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/parents/parents-association" class="">Parents&#39; Association</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/our-community/the-brentwood-school-podcast" class="">The Brentwood School Podcast</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/brentwood-school-ai-conference/brentwood-school-ai-conference" class="">Brentwood School AI Conference</a><ul><li><a href="/our-community/brentwood-school-ai-conference/brentwood-school-ai-conference" class="">Brentwood School AI Conference</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/brentwood-school-ai-conference/ai-in-education-conference-workshops" class="">AI in Education Conference: Workshops</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/our-community/diversity-inclusion" class="">Diversity &amp; Inclusion</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/school-development" class="">School Development</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/learning-community" class="">Learning Community</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/old-brentwoods" class="active">Old Brentwoods</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/foundation" class="">Foundation</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/charity" class="">Charity</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/spiritual-life" class="">Spiritual Life</a></li></ul></div><div class="slvl-content-section-sidebar-level slvl-sidepromo-section"><h2 class="slvl-content-section-sidebar-title slvl-sidepromo-title">Where Next?</h2><div class="slvl-sidepromo"><a href="/admissions/bursaries-scholarships" class="slvl-sidepromo-item">  <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/promos/Brentwood-Bursaries-White.png" alt="Bursaries img"> <span>Bursaries</span> </a> <a href="/contact" class="slvl-sidepromo-item">  <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/promos/Brentwood-Contact-White.png" alt="Contact img"> <span>Contact</span> </a> <a href="/we-are-brentwood/our-alumni" class="slvl-sidepromo-item">  <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/promos/Brentwood-OurAlumni-White.png" alt="Our Alumni img"> <span>Our Alumni</span> </a></div></div></div><div class="slvl-content-section-main"><ul class="slvl-content-breadcrumbs"><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li><a href="/our-community/parents" title="Our Community">Our Community</a></li><li title="Old Brentwoods">Old Brentwoods</li></ul><div class="secondLvlCss"><p><style>br{mso-data-placement:same-cell}</style></p><p>Once you&rsquo;ve been a pupil of Brentwood School, you will always remain part of our international community of&nbsp;Old Brentwoods (OBs).</p><p>We hope that your school days were some of the best days of your life and that you will stay in touch, keep us up-to-date with your achievements and come back to visit soon. In return, we&rsquo;ll update you with news of your former school friends, send you our annual School magazine &#39;The Brentwood School Times&#39;, invite you to special OB events and help you stay well-connected within the global community that is Old Brentwoods. &nbsp;</p><p>There are many ways to keep in touch and ensure your details are up-to-date. You can register&nbsp;on the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.oldbrentwoods.com/" target="_blank">Brentwood School Association website</a>, contact us by telephone <a href="tel:+44 (0)1277 240 452">+44 (0)1277 240 452</a>,&nbsp;email&nbsp;<a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#640b08000616010a10130b0b0017240616010a10130b0b004a011717011c4a17070c4a110f"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="5b34373f39293e352f2c34343f281b39293e352f2c34343f753e28283e2375283833752e30">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>&nbsp;or send in updates by post to the Development Office&nbsp;at the address below.</p><p>We look forward to hearing from you.</p><p style="text-align:center"><a class="downloadBtn" href="http://www.oldbrentwoods.com/" target="_blank">Register to be part of the OB Network</a></p><hr><h2>Our OB Community</h2><p><meta charset="utf-8">Our OB Community is a collaborative, supportive network for all our alumni, and it can sometimes help out in the most unlikely of places.<strong>&nbsp;</strong>A former student&nbsp;who had just graduated from university got in touch and asked if we knew any Old Brentwoods in Australia since he wanted to travel there and look for work.&nbsp;</p><p>We sent an email out to OBs living there and within a few hours, he had an offer of an apartment overlooking Sydney Harbour Bridge for two weeks!</p><p>This is just one example of how much Old Brentwoods are willing to help each other all over the world.</p><p><meta charset="utf-8"></p><p dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.oldbrentwoods.com" target="_blank">Join&nbsp;today</a> to have this thriving network at your fingertips.</p><p dir="ltr"><meta charset="utf-8"></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%"><thead><tr><th colspan="1" scope="col">Old Brentwoods President</th></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="/userfiles/bsmvc/body/05-our-community/body-christian-croll.jpg" style="margin:10px;width:30%"><br> The President&nbsp;for 2023-24&nbsp;<br> is Christian Croll (OB 1977-88).</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Body/05-Our-Community/body-jos-hollington.jpg" style="margin:10px;width:30%"><br> The President-Elect for 2023-24&nbsp;<br> is Jos Hollington (OB 1972-81).</td></tr></thead></table><h2 dir="ltr"><meta charset="utf-8">OB Clubhouse</h2><p dir="ltr"><img alt="photo of the old brentwood club house grounds" src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Body/05-Our-Community/body-ob-clubhouse-grounds.jpg" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;width:25%">The Old Brentwoods Club is a sport and social club with over 600 members playing and supporting a wide range of sports and activities. Located on Ashwells Road, Brentwood, is an excellent clubhouse with a spacious bar and social area, surrounded by over 20 acres of sports grounds and extensive on-site parking for players and supporters.&nbsp;</p><p dir="ltr">Whether you are presently a social member of the club, a member of one of the sports clubs, an Old Brentwood, parent of a pupil&nbsp;or a member of the public, you are able to book the clubhouse for a private function.&nbsp;</p><p dir="ltr"><a class="downloadBtn" href="http://www.oldbrentwoodsclub.org/" target="_blank">OldBrentwoodsClub.org</a></p><p dir="ltr"><meta charset="utf-8"></p><hr><h2 dir="ltr">Brentwood School Archives</h2><p dir="ltr">There is a wealth of invaluable resources for documenting the history of the School, its students&nbsp;and staff, in the School Archives, some of which can be found <a href="http://brentwood-heritage.daisy.websds.net/" target="_blank">on the Brentwood Heritage website</a>.&nbsp;</p><hr><h2>Brentwood School Times</h2><p>The Development Office produces an annual magazine for Old Brentwoods to enjoy, the Brentwood School Times. It includes a round-up of School life over the course of the past year, as well as lots of updates and success stories from OBs themselves.</p><p>All OBs are able to receive a postal copy of this magazine, as well as read the magazines below. If you would like to register your address for next year&rsquo;s edition, please do so <a href="http://www.oldbrentwoods.com" target="_blank">here</a>.</p></div><div class="portal-icon"><div><a href="https://www.brentwoodschool.co.uk/userfiles/bsmvc/Documents/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/document-brentwood-school-times-2023.pdf" target="_self" class="hasImage" title="BST 2023"> <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/promos/icons/iocn-bst-icon-2023.jpg?command_1=resize&amp;width_1=170" alt="BST 2023" title="BST 2023"> </a> <span><b>BST 2023</b></span></div><div><a href="https://www.brentwoodschool.co.uk/userfiles/bsmvc/Documents/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/document-bst-2022-interactive-version.pdf" target="_self" class="hasImage" title="BST 2022"> <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Body/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/icon-bst-2022.jpg?command_1=resize&amp;width_1=170" alt="BST 2022" title="BST 2022"> </a> <span><b>BST 2022</b></span></div><div><a href="/userfiles/bsmvc/Documents/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/document-BST-2021.pdf" target="_self" class="hasImage" title="BST 2021"> <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Body/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/iocn-bst-icon-2021.png?command_1=resize&amp;width_1=170" alt="BST 2021" title="BST 2021"> </a> <span><b>BST 2021</b></span></div><div><a href="/userfiles/bsmvc/Documents/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/document-brentwood-school-times-2020.pdf" target="_blank" class="hasImage" title="BST 2020"> <img src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Body/05-Our-Community/brentwood-school-times/iocn-bst-icon-2020.png?command_1=resize&amp;width_1=170" alt="BST 2020" title="BST 2020"> </a> <span><b>BST 2020</b></span></div></div><div class="secondLvlCss"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%"><thead><tr><th colspan="1" scope="col" style="text-align:center">Contact Us</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="/userfiles/bsmvc/Images/Body/01-we-are-brentwood/slt/Sam%20Mason.jpg" style="width:20%"></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center;vertical-align:top"><p><strong>Mr Sam Mason</strong><br> <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#5835392b37362b183a2a3d362c2f37373c763d2b2b3d20762b3b30762d33672b2d3a323d3b2c650f3d3a2b312c3d7d6a681d36292d312a21"><span class="_